# Project Name: AI-Powered Code Builder & Secure Portfolio Manager  

## Core Features  
1. **AI Code Generator**  
   - NLP-powered code suggestions  
   - Autocomplete for multiple programming languages  

2. **Portfolio & Financial Management**  
   - Secure repository for code snippets  
   - Income/expense tracking for freelancers  
   - Project-based earnings visualization  

3. **Security & Compliance**  
   - End-to-end encryption  
   - GDPR & SOC2 compliance  
   - Role-based access controls  

4. **Integration & Collaboration**  
   - GitHub/GitLab integration  
   - Secure file sharing & collaboration  

5. **User Experience & Interface**  
   - Clean dashboard with analytics  
   - Mobile & desktop compatibility  

## Tech Stack  
- **Backend:** Python (Django/FastAPI), Node.js  
- **Frontend:** React.js, Next.js, Tailwind CSS  
- **Database:** PostgreSQL, Firebase, or MongoDB  
- **Security:** AES-256 Encryption, OAuth2, MFA  
- **Hosting:** AWS/GCP/DigitalOcean  

## Monetization Strategy  
- Subscription model (Freemium + Premium)  
- Pay-per-use AI code generation credits  
- Custom enterprise solutions  

## Development Roadmap  
1. **MVP Development** (3-6 months)  
   - AI code builder  
   - Secure storage & authentication  
2. **Beta Testing & Feedback** (1-2 months)  
3. **Scaling & Feature Expansion**  
   - Financial tracking & analytics  
   - Team collaboration tools  
4. **Marketing & Launch Strategy**  
   - Target developers & freelancers  
   - Partnership with coding bootcamps  

## Security Measures  
- **Data Encryption:** AES-256 at rest, TLS in transit  
- **Authentication:** OAuth2, 2FA/MFA  
- **Compliance:** GDPR, CCPA, SOC2  


